creator: Seri-Safe LLC
descriptionHtml:
➢ Seri-Safe is a program that allows individuals and businesses to create a cloud inventory and detailed list of your valuable possessions by storing the serial number and photos across all mobile platforms

➢ We can offer it to pawn shops to check against our individual and business databases to ensure they are not receiving stolen property and lowering the risk of profits loss

➢ We can offer it to individuals and businesses to catalogue in detail serial numbers, photos and specific description of valuable items at risk of being stolen

➢ We can offer it to law enforcement to help track down stolen property and get faster notification of an item if it has been stolen and or surfaces.

➢ Seri-Safe also lets you run a check on items in our database that you may be skeptical of buying from a third-party via in person or online.

➢ (note: users do not have access to other user databases. Each database is secure and confidential. The only way an item will appear to all users, is if the item has been tagged as stolen by the individual account holder.)

title: Seri-Safe

creator: Seri-Safe LLC
descriptionHtml:
Seri-Safe: Cloud Asset Inventory Keeper and Tracker App for you!

If you are looking for a Cloud Asset Management app that allows you to create cloud inventory and detailed list of your valuable assets by storing the serial number and photos across mobile apps and websites, then this Stock and Inventory Cloud App is for you.

How This Cloud Asset Inventory Tracker & Manager App Works:


Seri-Safe comes with a really smart inventory system that will allow you to list all your valuable assets with serial number. You can also add photos of your items to recognize them easily. Open a free account with only your email address and start listing your valuable items in the app. Add a serial number, purchase date, item type, and a short description along with a photo. If you are looking for an Asset Store app for asset tracking for personal or business purpose, this app can be a great tool for you. You can also keep track of raw material inventory of your business or household items.

Whether it’s personal inventory of value or your business assets, you can keep track of everything through this stock controller and manager app. Collecting and tracking valuable assets have never been easier as it is with this new cloud-based stock and inventory tracker app. You can use it for both business and home inventory management. You don’t have to keep a separate inward outward register or item management book if you have this efficient and smart app.

What Purpose Does It Serve:


➢ If you are looking for a personal or shop stock maintain app that allows you to create a cloud inventory with detailed list of your items, then this app is for you.

➢ This cloud based asset tracker app allows pawn shops to check against our individual and business databases to ensure you are not receiving stolen property and lowering the risk of profits loss. We keep items stock record to keep you safe!

➢ You can list your physical inventory with a serial number, description, with photos. It’s a catalogue app that allows you to item stock record with every necessary details to reduce the risk of being stolen.

➢ The law enforcement officials can use this stock maintain software to track down stolen assets quickly. They will get notification when an item gets stolen or surfaces.

➢ If you are skeptical of an item you are skeptical about buying, you can run a check through our database to be sure.

Some Key Features of the Seri-Safe Cloud Inventory Tracker App:


** List Your Asset Perfectly:


This Cloud-based Item Management app allows you to list all your valuable assets with serial number, description, and photo to properly keep track of your items. You can see all your items at a glance with every necessary details from this app with ease.

** Easy to Use:


Entering an item and keeping track of them through this inventory management app is really easy. There’s no complicated procedure to list and track your valuable assets. Everything is in front of you, and you can contact us anytime for any help.

** A Cross-Platform Product Stock Maintain and Tracking App:


This efficient and simple stock maintain software will allow you to manage and track everything through multiple devices from one single account. You can use the Android app, iOS app, and web service (via seri-safe.com). We bring you the ultimate convenience when it comes to tracking your valuable assets.

** A Safe Space with Convenience:


Users do not have access to other user databases. Each database is secure and confidential. The only way an item will appear to all users, is if the item has been tagged as stolen by the individual account holder. Therefore, you can still keep your items safe through this app without exposing your entire database to others.

Download the Seri-Safe: Cloud Asset Inventory Keeper and Tracker app to manage your valuable assets like never before!
